1942;;The Bugle Sounds;;American;;S. Sylvan Simon;;Wallace Beery, Marjorie Main, Donna Reed;;war;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Bugle_Sounds;;In 1941, Colonel Lawton (Lewis Stone) of the 19th Cavalry Regiment has to convert his unit from horses to tanks. Sergeant Patrick Aloysius 'Hap' Doan (Wallace Beery) has a hard time with the adjustments.